reviewText: It's ok... She likes it and understood to peepee in potty.. But this had me a bit worried in the beginning since it kept mentioning the diaper and she wanted the diaper too.. But then she did see that they were using the potty and she did want to use it but still had the diapers in mind... I wish that they didn't have an accent just because I had problems understanding .. Would have wanted it a bit longer.. Or maybe another episode..
Not worth the money, creepy video, did not meet expectations.
My toddlers LOVE this movie and sing the catchy songs all day long. It's a very helpful video for those pooty training there tots. Highly recommended.
